				<staticText>
					<reportElement uuid="73b5129a-3df7-4877-bcee-ec5ba5770436" style="Defaultback_42020190" mode="Opaque" x="134" y="375" width="413" height="85" forecolor="#000000" backcolor="#FFFFFF">
						<property name="com.cabsoft.rx.export.html.zindex" value="1"/>
					</reportElement>
					<box leftPadding="2">
						<leftPen lineWidth="0.75"/>
						<bottomPen lineWidth="0.75"/>
					</box>
					<textElement textAlignment="Left" verticalAlignment="Middle" markup="html">
						<font size="6" isBold="false"/>
					</textElement>
					<text><![CDATA[■ <b>신용정보집중기관 및 신용조회회사에 대한 제공 :</b> • 신용정보집중기관 [전국은행연합회, 여신금융협회 등]<br>
&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
• 신용조회회사 [서울신용평가정보(주), 코리아크레딧뷰로(주), NICE신용평가정보(주) 등]<br>
■ <b>금융거래의 설정·유지·이행·관리 등에 필요한 업무를 수행하는 제휴업체 : </b>LIG 손해보험(주), 서울보증보험, ㈜동부화재해상보험 등<br>
■ <b>수탁업체에 대한 제공 : </b>가람감정평가법인, 가온감정평가법인, 경일감정평가법인, 나라감정평가법인, 대일감정원,  대한감정평가법인,<br>
&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
 대화감정평가법인,미래새한감정평가법인, 미래신용정보㈜, 빌포스트㈜, 삼일감정평가법인, 삼일회계법인, 삼창감정평가법인,<br>
&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
 서울신용평가정보㈜,써브감정평가법인,솔로몬신용정보㈜,  신한신용정보㈜,  에이원감정평가법인,  제일감정평가법인, ㈜그린CS,<br>
&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
 ㈜비포스, ㈜신한데이타시스템, ㈜신한서브,(주)아데코코리아, ㈜아이앤씨엠, ㈜엠피씨, ㈜제니엘, 중앙감정평가법인, <br>
&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
태평양감정평가법인, 통일감정평가법인, 프라임감정평가법인, 하나감정평가법인,한신정신용정보㈜, 효성ITX㈜ 등
]]></text>
				</staticText>
				<staticText>
					<reportElement uuid="73b5129a-3df7-4877-bcee-ec5ba5770436" style="Defaultback_42020190" mode="Opaque" x="34" y="460" width="100" height="27" forecolor="#000000" backcolor="#CCCCCC">
